@startuml
title Feature 013 - профиль и настройки пользователя

actor "Покупатель/партнер" as User
actor "Оператор поддержки" as Support
participant "Frontend web-shell" as FE
participant "profile controller" as ProfileController
participant "profile service" as ProfileService
database "profile DB" as ProfileDb
participant "order/claim flows" as OrderFlows
participant "auth/security context" as Auth

User -> FE: Открывает /profile-settings
FE -> ProfileController: GET /api/profile
ProfileController -> Auth: Проверить текущего пользователя
ProfileController -> ProfileService: loadOverview(currentUser)
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Прочитать profile, contacts, addresses, documents, events
ProfileService -> ProfileService: Рассчитать readiness и masked values
ProfileService --> ProfileController: ProfileOverviewResponse
ProfileController --> FE: sections, readiness, mnemonic codes
FE --> User: Показывает обзор профиля

User -> FE: Сохраняет general/contact/address/document section
FE -> ProfileController: PUT/POST /api/profile/** + Idempotency-Key
ProfileController -> Auth: Проверить ownership
ProfileController -> ProfileService: validateAndSave(sectionPayload)
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Сохранить изменения секции
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Записать profile_audit_event
ProfileService --> ProfileController: Updated section response
ProfileController --> FE: masked values, section status, message mnemo
FE --> User: Показывает результат сохранения

User -> FE: Меняет пароль
FE -> ProfileController: POST /api/profile/security/password
ProfileController -> Auth: Проверить текущего пользователя/challenge
ProfileController -> ProfileService: changePassword(request)
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Записать profile_security_event и audit event
ProfileService --> ProfileController: success or STR_MNEMO_PROFILE_PASSWORD_WEAK
ProfileController --> FE: status / mnemonic
FE --> User: Показывает локализованный результат

OrderFlows -> ProfileController: GET /api/profile/readiness?flow=CHECKOUT|CLAIM
ProfileController -> ProfileService: evaluateReadiness(currentUser, flow)
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Прочитать обязательные секции
ProfileService --> ProfileController: ProfileReadinessResponse
ProfileController --> OrderFlows: ready, missingFields, messageMnemo

Support -> FE: Открывает support view профиля с reason
FE -> ProfileController: GET /api/profile/support/{userId}?reason=PROFILE_HELP
ProfileController -> Auth: Проверить support permission
ProfileController -> ProfileService: loadSupportView(userId, reason)
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Записать support audit event
ProfileService -> ProfileDb: Прочитать профиль без secrets
ProfileService --> ProfileController: ProfileOverviewResponse(auditRecorded=true)
ProfileController --> FE: masked support profile
FE --> Support: Показывает разрешенный support view
@enduml
